title.57: The Mutant Misadventures of Cloak and Dagger (1988) #14

description.0: Matt finds a new profession in the ring, while Bullseye expands his crime spree under the guise of Daredevil.
description.1: Nightcrawler's attempt at a relaxing weekend takes a turn for the worse when he crashes on a less-than tropical island!
description.2: The Gray Hulk, Betty and Rick Jones take on the Super-Skrull!
description.3: With Iron Man's body under the control of Kearson DeWitt, the mad scientist moves on to the next stage of his plan. Will Tony Stark manage to escape DeWitt's villainous grasp?
description.4: Wolverine succumbs to jungle madness as he tracks down drug dealers in Madripoor. Will Archie Corrigan and Tyger Tyger remain in the custody of kidnappers? Poison commits murder, while Scarlet Witch embraces her piratical side in her own swashbuckling adventure. Plus, a spotlight on Michael Collins, aka Deathlok.
description.5: Torment Part 4.  Writer/Artist Todd McFarlane puts his superstar stamp on Spider-Man with this classic story.  Has Kraven the Hunter returned?  Has be joined the Lizard?  Spider-Man is about to find out the hard way!
description.6: While the All-Father recovers in the Odinsleep, Heimdall is left to rule Asgard and rebuild the legendary Bifrost!
description.10: Stranded on a prehistoric island with no powers, the FF are in a race against tmie to escape the island before it fades into prehistory forever! But can they find a way off and avoid getting eaten at the same time?
description.12: Never say Logan isn't a good actor! After playing dead, Wolvie finds himself in Japan…seeking revenge on the Yakuza thugs who nearly killed him.
description.16: What if the Vision conquered the world? Succeeding where his father Ultron had failed countless times, the Vision takes over the world. When even the likes of Doctor Doom are made to accept the Vision as his ruler, what chance does the world have?
description.21: Castle infiltrates a military institution that may be a producer and supplier of child pornography.
description.23: Conan is a legend but sometimes even legends must die!
description.24: Introducing the Abominatrix! And she's going punch for punch with the jade giantess She-Hulk!
description.25: Mutant martial arts, the Puppet Master, and a race of green alien snails... this issue has it all!
description.28: Spider-Man no more! Peter Parker lets Doctor Turner remove his powers following a heated battle with the Femme Fatales. Too bad Tarantula is back on the scene, and is primed to squash Spidey!
description.29: The Avengers finish up modifications on their new Avengers Complex. But when two uninvited guests crash the front gate, will the team re-consider a new security system? Featuring Rage and the irradiated anti-hero, Ramskov!
description.30: Quasar and Cap team up against the super-powered Nefarius! Plus a solo Diamondback story.
description.32: The Machinesmith, Minister Blood, and Mother Night crash Sersi's party at Avengers Mansion. Will the team be able to keep themselves, and their partygoers, out of harm's way?
description.33: Nick Fury guest-stars! Three women threaten to tamper with New York City's water, and Punisher and Fury are hot to their plot!
description.34: THE FALL OF DOCTOR STRANGE! Dormammu has destroyed Strange's powers, leaving him helpless. But the question remains -- WHO WILL BE THE SORCEROR SUPREME?
description.37: Greg Salinger, A.K.A. the mania-prone Fool Killer, awakens in an insane asylum. Meanwhile, Kurt Gerhardt comes to his senses (or loses them entirely), following the violent death of his father. From the trenches of insanity, a new Fool Killer rises.
description.39: Anti-heroine Poison brings her toxic charm to Marvel Comics Presents! In one of her strangest battles yet, Scarlet Witch embodies a pirate ancestor. Doctor Strange encounters a woman from his past. But is this reunion welcome? Find out, in the magically-charged issue featuring your favorite Marvel mystics!
description.40: The Punisher becomes entrenched in an international incident when crime boss Hamilton "Bo" Greaves makes a crafty escape to Puerto Salvaje. But Frank Castle never loses a trail...
description.41: Torment Part 3.  Writer/Artist Todd McFarlane puts his superstar stamp on Spider-Man with this classic story.  The Lizard has Spider-Man defeated and moves in for the kill…but the Spider must suffer more first. As poison circulates through his body, Spider-Man faces his worst nightmare.
description.42: Torment Part 3.  Writer/Artist Todd McFarlane puts his superstar stamp on Spider-Man with this classic story.  The Lizard has Spider-Man defeated and moves in for the kill…but the Spider must suffer more first. As poison circulates through his body, Spider-Man faces his worst nightmare.
description.45: What if the Fantastic Four battled Doctor Doom before they got their powers? A duplicitous Victor Von Doom steals Reed's technology to save his mother from Mephisto, but when his plan fails, he blames Reed.
description.49: Spider-Man's close brushes with death have left him fearful for his loved ones. Will Peter Parker regain his normalcy once more? The Femme Fatales may change Spidey's mind about removing his powers...especially when the villainesses show the wall-crawler what they're made of!
description.50: The Avengers must work with Atalanteans and members of the Peace Corpse to escape Shaman's medicine pouch before it's too late! Will the Avengers, their allies, and their enemies, remain in a dimensional pocket for all time?
description.51: The epic conclusion to Kingpin versus Redskull! Plus: Stripped of the Super-Soldier serum-Cap fights for his life against Crossbones!
description.54: Punisher's face is left worse off than before when he and Jigsaw duel for the second time… but a recovery comes from the most unexpected of sources.
description.56: Conan versus his best friend, Jormma, in a fight to the death!
description.58: Enter Dorkum Asylum, home of the criminally insane. And meet it's newest resident…She-Hulk?! Held hostage by Jack Serious, it can only be Nosferata who can rescue Jen now!
description.59: The full story behind Alex’s horrifying demise! Enter: the Circus of Crime!
description.61: Bullseye masquerades as Daredevil! Matt tries to crack the case of his identity.
description.62: Excalibur agrees to help Alex Power when his siblings go missing in Nightmare's realm!
description.63: Meggan trashes Alistaire's birthday party when she transforms into a vampire! Doctor Strange makes a house call to get to the bottom of this odd happening.
description.64: Newly reunited lovers Bruce and Betty set out looking for their friend, Rick Jones. Little do they know he's been captured by an all too familiar enemy...
description.65: After Iron Man's battle against the Living Laser is over, he soon finds out that Kearson Dewitt has been behind everything! Will the Iron Avenger figure out a way to defeat his crafty new enemies at Marrs Corporations? Plus: Mandarin awakens Fin Fang Foom!
description.66: ON THE ROAD PART 7 Wolverine and Hulk star in their own road trippin' adventure, but not in the way you think. Scarlet Witch must confront the darkest parts of her past. What horrific hexes have led Wanda Maximoff to become the woman, and Avenger, she is today?
description.67: Torment Part 3.  Writer/Artist Todd McFarlane puts his superstar stamp on Spider-Man with this classic story.  The Lizard has Spider-Man defeated and moves in for the kill…but the Spider must suffer more first. As poison circulates through his body, Spider-Man faces his worst nightmare.
description.68: The birth of a Celestial! As the newest member of the cosmic Eternals is born, Stellaris makes her move to stop it!
description.69: Thor, Hercules, and Eric Masterson return from the Black Galaxy, only to find two ancient enemies of Asgard locked in combat - Surtur of the Flame, and Ymir of the Frost!
description.73: Before the FF can get back to the present, they get stranded in time on an island of dinosaurs! And if that's not bad enough, the team's powers have all stopped working!
description.74: Rogue has returned to the X-Men's base in the Australian outback after being spat out by the Siege Perilous. However, her return is met with bad news and a team in disarray. Rogue must battle the life-force of Carol Danvers after losing some of her Ms. Marvel abilities.
description.75: Wolverine, usually not one to be on the losing end of any battle, finds himself in a fever dream within a coma. The villains who haunt his dreams cannot be killed, no matter how much Logan wishes them dead.
description.80: In an effort to save Steve Rogers' life, Hank Pym must cleanse the Sentinel of Liberty's bloodstream! However, this may cause the super-soldier formula to disappear as well. Plus: The Kingpin and Red Skull continue their turf war in New York.
description.81: With Jim Lee drawing Captain America, Black Widow, and Wolverine ready to kick ass what more could you ask for?  Rogue in a bikini you say?  Well maybe you're right but this cover is still awesome.
description.82: Logan is dressed as his alter ego, Patch, when a very suspicious group walks into his bar…We promise that's not the set-up to a bad joke.
description.84: Shaman of Alpha Flight saves the day when he contains a nuclear explosion in his mystical medicine pouch. The only problem? The Avengers are now trapped in the dimensional pockets of the pouch, alongside heavy doses of radiation and the madmen who planted the bomb!
description.85: Punisher seeks aid within a Mayan temple to restore his face after Jigsaw’s brutal slashing!
description.87: The Terminus Factor Part 4. The original Terminus vs the offspring of Terminus… with the Avengers in the middle!  The prize? Earth itself!
description.88: The return of DORMAMMU! The lord of the Dark Dimension has not only sent his Mindless Ones to plague New York City, he also has Clea as his captive!
description.93: Who is Jack Murdock? Daredevil gets a bad case of amnesia upon his return from Hell. Bullseye swoops in for the kill.
description.94: Phoenix and Nightcrawler - with nowhere to escape! When led to a TV studio, the pair of mutants get whisked away to another dimension, where they must face a mysterious new foe! Who is the NTH MAN?
description.95: Excalibur hits up the night life! Captain Britain and Meggan decide to take a well-earned break and go out on the town, but trouble STILL manages to find them! Can Meggan manage to survive bar brawls with sleazy crooks AND make it through her first drink?
description.96: Bruce and Betty rekindle their romance after finding humor in their mutual situations. All of this despite being trapped inside a convent...with Doc Samson's fleet barricaded outside!
description.97: Tony Stark is being attacked on all sides. The Mandarin! The Living Laser! Titanium Man! Marrs Corporation! All evil! And all want Tony Stark's head!
description.99: Torment Part 2.  Writer/Artist Todd McFarlane puts his superstar stamp on Spider-Man with this classic story.  The Lizard has left a calling card at one of his murder scenes and Spider-Man leaps into the chase to find him.  A bloody battle ensues, but how can Spider-Man stop the Lizard when he feels no pain and refuses to be stopped?

5.text: TORMENT PART FOUR Has Kraven the Hunter returned? Has he joined the Lizard? Spider-Man is about to find out the hard way!
TORMENT PART FOUR Has Kraven the Hunter returned? Has he joined the Lizard? Spider-Man is about to find out the hard way!

8.text: X-Factor is briefed on their mission-to fight their way through Genosha and save their fellow mutants!

11.text: Storm's child body may be permanent, which doesn't bode well for the X-Men, as the Genoshan troops are on the offensive-with Havok on their side?!

12.text: Never say Logan isn't a good actor! After playing dead, Wolvie finds himself in Japan…seeking revenge on the Yakuza thugs who nearly killed him.

14.text: The strange saga of the Silver Surfer in Dynamo City continues as he finds himself at the mercy of…lawyers?

15.text: The Great Lakes Avengers ATTACK Captain America! But why?

19.text: Namor…grounded! Following his battle with Sluj, Namor’s wings have fallen off leaving the Sub-Mariner flightless! But he won’t have time to mourn this tragic loss -- enter the Headhunter!

20.text: The search for Midnight continues! Guest-starring Spider-Man and the Punisher.

22.text: Brute Force and Heavy Metal battle head-to-head once and for all!

24.text: Introducing the Abominatrix! And she's going punch for punch with the Jade Giantess She-Hulk!

27.text: The new Ghost Rider, Danny Ketch, has his first run-in with one of Marvel's most fearsome villains - the twisted serial killer, Scarecrow.

31.text: Vance Astro has lost Captain America's shield to his enemies. Can he reclaim it or will he succumb to the Force?

34.text: THE FALL OF DOCTOR STRANGE! Dormammu has destroyed Strange's powers, leaving him helpless. But the question remains -- WHO WILL BE THE SORCEROR SUPREME?

35.text: After defeating their first threat, the New Warriors don't have a chance to catch their breaths as Psionex, a new group with the intention of crushing the team, emerges into the fray.

36.text: Can Sunspot, Rictor and Wolfsbane stop Cable and Wolverine from tearing eachother apart?

37.text: Greg Salinger, A.K.A. the mania-prone Fool Killer, awakens in an insane asylum. Meanwhile, Kurt Gerhardt comes to his senses (or loses them entirely), following the violent death of his father. From the trenches of insanity, a new Fool Killer rises.

38.text: Apogee of Disaster Part 2. When a terrifying threat emerges in space, Fury grabs his spacesuit and takes off!

43.text: Ghost Rider vs. The Punisher: Round Two! Two of Marvel's grittiest anti-heroes go head-to-flaming skull...just before the Flag-Smasher makes the mistake of intervening.

44.text: New Yorker Human Torch may have to transition to the west coast lifestyle! Will he accept his invitation to join the West Coast Avengers?!

46.text: At Quasar's request, Overmind tries to draw out the Stranger by threatening the Squadron.

52.text: Appearing from the ocean’s murkiest depths he is… Sluj! And this mucky monster is putting the passengers of the Sea Queen in grave danger!

53.text: Guest starring Spider-Man and the Punisher! This trio sets out to topple the new Secret Empire ... if they can keep from fighting each other!

55.text: With the wildest world-polluting agent set on destruction, Brute Force must come together and stop this millionaire-gone-mad!

57.text: Cloak and Dagger deal with a gang that is skewering people!

58.text: Enter Dorkum Asylum, home of the criminally insane. And meet it's newest resident…She-Hulk?! Held hostage by Jack Serious, it can only be Nosferata who can rescue Jen now!

67.text: TORMENT PART THREE Calypso controls the Lizard! What does she hope to gain from this terrible and vicious battle, where the claw and tooth of the lizard rends the web of the spider? Can Spidey make it out alive or will the streets run red with his blood?

75.text: Wolverine, usually not one to be on the losing end of any battle, finds himself in a fever dream within a coma. The villains who haunt his dreams cannot be killed, no matter how much Logan wishes them dead.

77.text: The Surfer is forced to extend his stay in Dynamo City -- plus, Drax the Destroyer shares some distressing news.

78.text: The final battle! Deathlok is joined by Sunfire in his fight against Roxxon Oil!

79.text: The Guardians battle the Force, their villainous counterparts!

81.text: With Jim Lee drawing Captain America, Black Widow, and Wolverine ready to kick butt what more could you ask for?

82.text: Logan is dressed as his alter ego, Patch, when a very suspicious group walks into his bar…We promise that's not the set-up to a bad joke.

83.text: THE RETURN OF THE SINISTER SIX PART 6 Doctor Octopus plans to release a deadly poison into Earth's atmosphere so that he can instate himself and the Sinister Six as the world's new leaders! Can Spidey stop the Sinister Six?

86.text: THE RETURN OF THE SINISTER SIX PART 5 Doctor Octopus' plan for the Sinister Six is finally revealed!

87.text: The Terminus Factor Part 4. The original Terminus vs the offspring of Terminus… with the Avengers in the middle!  The prize? Earth itself!

88.text: The return of DORMAMMU! The lord of the Dark Dimension has not only sent his Mindless Ones to plague New York City, he also has Clea as his captive!

89.text: Apogee of Disaster Part 1. Guest-starring the Fantastic Four!

90.text: Things go from bad to worse as the New Warriors square off against the Mad Thinker and Primus! With little experience working together, will they defeat this new threat? What does Night Thrasher know about the pair that he is unwilling to share?

91.text: A historic battle: Cable versus Wolverine! This issue also features Sunfire!

99.text: TORMENT PART TWO Peter Parker and Mary Jane are spending some time together when their pleasant evening is interrupted by a news report detailing a new murder, presumably committed by the Lizard. Spidey sets out to investigate! Prepare for a bloody battle!
